                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caesar</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Lic</abbr><ex>inio</ex></expan> Gall&amp;lt;i&amp;gt;en<surplus>i</surplus>o <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>elici</ex></expan> invicto <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>pontef</abbr><ex>ico</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> proco<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> de<lb break="no" n="6"/>dicante <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Victore <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> per <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Dometia<lb break="no" n="10"/>no <note>sic</note> |(centurionem) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praep</abbr><ex>ositum</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>red</abbr><ex>ucum</ex></expan> devotus <lb n="12"/>numini ipsius <lb n="13"/>de qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>estura</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> <lb n="14"/>posuit </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Posita VI Idus Octobres <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>IO<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>AV</del> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></del>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung für eine Mauer innerhalb des Kastells. Auf der Oberseite drei Dübellöcher und Einlassungen für die Füße einer Bronzestatue. Die Inschrift verteilt sich auf die Vorder- (Z. 1-16) und linke Nebenseite (Z. 17-19); Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona, Z. 16 auf der crepido. Z. 1-15 stehen auf Rasur einer älteren Inschrift, zu der auch Z. 16 und Z. 17-19 gehören. Z. 18-19: noch einige nicht mehr identifizierbare Buchstabenreste erhalten. Datierung: wegen Augg(ustorum) (Z. 9) nicht nach 260 n. Chr. (B): Hristov; Eck - Ivanov: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
